{"tid":2300592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國軍預告修體位區分標準 身高155到157公分男子也要當兵了","createTime":"2020-11-25T15:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T04:27:12.000Z","uid":56533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddca37a645bbf05abf70b120ce4eee3873e7be5f","tid":2300592,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:49:10.000Z","msg":"未來服役體位身高標準將有變化！國防部今天表示，鑑因現今作戰型態改變，視力、BMI 值及身高已非服兵役限制條件，基於兵役公平原則，預告修正「體位區分標準」，<span class=\"red\">役男免役身高從原來的157公分，下修為未滿155公分</span>；視力方面，不僅考量散瞳後的驗光度數與兩眼度數相差，更加註「最佳矯正視力未達0.6者」才能免役。<br />\n<br />\n依照國防部規定，身高測定採立姿，以公分為單位，未達1 公分之尾數不計，如154.1 公分或154.9 公分均以154 公分計；<span class=\"red\">身高196 公分以上或身高154 公分以下者，屬免役體位。</span><br />\n<br />\n國防部現行「體位區分標準」第2條規定附件的規定，達適服役年齡的男子，若身高196公分以上、157公分以下者免役。但此次新修訂的標準，則是將免役身高調整至154公分以下，除非BMI（身體質量指數）未滿16.5或大於35才得以免役。<br />\n<br />\n國防部表示，現行「體位區分標準」是國防部與內政部在2018年修正發布，但考量當前作戰型態的改變，才以預告修正「體位區分標準」第2條附件的規定，各界人士對公告內容如有意見或疑問，請於本公告刊登於行政院公報之日起 60 日內（即2021年1月22日），以電話：02-85099272、傳真：02-85099274；或是電子信箱：nycall@gmail.com的方式陳述意見。<br />\n<br />\n國防部強調，修訂「體位區分標準」非因役男招募不足，是因應作戰型態改變，及廣儲後備的需求，須重新檢討兵役限制條件，基於兵役公平原則，因此研擬修正役男體位標準。國防部指出，已初步召集內政部役政署、訓練單位，以及各專科醫學會研討後，暫訂調整役男體位區分標準，尚未完成定案。<br />\n<br />\n國防部表示，修正草案將公告60天，期間廣蒐各方意見，後續再召集相關單位進行研討，以臻周延。（王烱華／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201125/2PQODEF4KJGKDKFPVQDQ4FJS3M/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DrWDiYHNN7JjN_p2YZPlLOOAzzbl2tvJQT-uI-evN_T-K_o9mxp4bDrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201125%2F2PQODEF4KJGKDKFPVQDQ4FJS3M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DrWDiYHNN7JjN_p2YZPlLOOAzzbl2tvJQT-uI-evN_T-K_o9mxp4bDrE&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=d7f51cb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201125%2F2PQODEF4KJGKDKFPVQDQ4FJS3M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1DrWDiYHNN7JjN_p2YZPlLOOAzzbl2tvJQT-uI-evN_T-K_o9mxp4bDrE&h=e7ece86b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201125/2PQODEF4KJGKDKFPVQDQ4FJS3M/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1DrWDiYHNN7JjN_p2YZPlLOOAzzbl2tvJQT-uI-evN_T-K_o9mxp4bDrE</a>"},{"pid":"dd353f31515f22485f65c3ca766bae638cefab63","tid":2300592,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"仆街, 真係台海危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff21055b867c8076307119d953ac482fce64ae8","tid":2300592,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"傷殘人士都要服兵役<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f6216f181a7f9851e36f01b2e6cd3b7b324cf","tid":2300592,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"天下JER霸都冇得免役<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d2dbf1dea141c457ce72cff04bdccea55c6cb4","tid":2300592,"uid":66527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"香港人想過去服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a98321f459782df297622397b1fd2a8c0c620d","tid":2300592,"uid":344567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"咁不如徵d 165以上嘅女人"},{"pid":"c39977318efa18931f8641ef856064833de0b926","tid":2300592,"uid":3649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"台灣依家啲兵役扣埋放假，<br />\n唔洗一年就出返嚟<br />\n<br />\n見啲台仔好多一生朋友都係做「阿兵哥」嗰陣識返嚟，<br />\n以前住台灣成日聽佢哋講當兵啲蝦碌嘢"},{"pid":"fbe9297db2ba12c4cb0e82dc92928812f7904cdf","tid":2300592,